snippet.title: Cod Quest | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
💪 Run, grow and defend the UK's last fish and chip shop. Your chippy is under threat from an impending invasion; you have 30 days to prepare. Upgrade your plot, unlock better recipes, purchase new equipment and more! 🐟
